f CrossFit)</span></p>\\r\\n</blockquote>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\\r\\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\\r\\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\\r\\n<h1\n    id=\\\"coaches\\\">Coaches</h1>\\r\\n<p><img style=\\\"float: right;\\\" src=\\\"../../../../../system/cms/files/files/000/000/003/original/dom.png\\\"\n    alt=\\\"Dom\\\" width=\\\"325\\\" height=\\\"312\\\" /></p>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\\r\\n<h3>Dominic\n    Morisi</h3>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Age: 27</li>\\r\\n<li>Experience:</li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>5\n    Years of CrossFit</li>\\r\\n<li>5 Years of Coaching</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n<li>Certifications:</li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>NFPT\n    (2009)</li>\\r\\n<li>CrossFit Level1(2011)</li>\\r\\n<li>USAW Level1 (2012)</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n<p>My\n    name is Dominic Morisi, and I was born and raised in Baltimore. I am 27 years\n    old and newly married. I fell in love with CrossFit in 2008. My first WOD was\n    FightGoneBad, which destroyed me. Since that first taste of iron in my throat,\n    I have been completely hooked. I enjoy every aspect of CrossFit, from heavy squats\n    to the handstand pushup, but the community is what I live for. I have been a personal\n    trainer since February 2009 and in January 2011 decided to start working for myself\n    and training out of my garage. Since then, I have built a small community of fitness\n    enthusiasts which I intend to grow large and still keep that small family feel!</p>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\\r\\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\\r\\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\\r\\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\\r\\n<p><img\n    style=\\\"float: left;\\\" src=\\\"../../../../../system/cms/files/files/000/000/004/original/tony.png\\\"\n    alt=\\\"tony\\\" width=\\\"323\\\" height=\\\"307\\\" /></p>\\r\\n<h3>Anthony Morisi</h3>\\r\\n<ul\n    style=\\\"margin-left: 350px;\\\">\\r\\n<li>Age: 31</li>\\r\\n<li>Experience:</li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>5\n    Years of CrossFit</li>\\r\\n<li>1 Year of Coaching</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n<li>Certifications:</li>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>CrossFit\n    Level 1 (2012)</li>\\r\\n<li>USAW Level 1 (2012)</li>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n</ul>\\r\\n<p>In\n    the Spring of 2008, I started my career as a firefighter. I was looking for a\n    fitness program that would prepare me, physically and mentally, for the rigors\n    of my new career. This was when I found CrossFit. In CrossFit, I found a training\n    program and methodology that challenged me constantly and developed the functional\n    fitness that I needed to take on my new career as well as everything that else\n    life had in store for me. I had found a new passion that was all about, hard work,\n    mental toughness and community. My passion for CrossFit has changed my life. &nbsp;Now,\n    as a coach, I love seeing the change in others as we grow our community of fit,\n    accountable, and confident human beings.</p>\\r\\n<script>// <![CDATA[\\r\\n$(function(){\\r\\n$(\\\"#map\\\").click(\\r\\n\n    \\       function() {\\r\\n            console.log(\\\"hover over\\\");\\r\\n            $(this).stop().animate({width:\n    \\\"600px\\\", height: \\\"600px\\\"}, 1000);\\r\\n        },\\r\\n        function() {\\r\\n\n    \\           console.log(\\\"hover out\\\");\\r\\n            $(this).stop().animate({width:\n    \\\"300px\\\", height: \\\"300px\\\"}, 1000);\\r\\n        }\\r\\n)});\\r\\n// ]]></script>\"\n','2013-11-29 23:05:47'),(26,'Cms::Page',5,'---\nblocks_attributes:\n- :identifier: content\n  :content: \"<h1 id=\\\"location\\\">Location</h1>\\r\\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<div\n    id=\\\"map\\\"><img src=\\\"../../../../../system/cms/files/files/000/000/005/original/cfb.png\\\"\n    alt=\\\"map\\\" /></div>\\r\\n<div style=\\\"vertical-align: middle; font-size: 18pt;\n    text-align: center; display: table-cell; padding-left: 20px;\\\">\\r\\n<div>2914 Sylvan\n    Ave <br />Baltimore, MD 21214</div>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n</div>\\r\\n<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\\r\\n<h1\n    id=\\\"crossfit\\\">What is Crossfit?</h1>\\r\\